# 04 — Realtime & Messaging

Ôn **WebSocket**, **Kafka**, **WebRTC signaling** — bám CV (5k connections, Kafka, WebRTC crash → WebSocket routing).

## Kiến thức cần cover

- **WebSocket:** Handshake, heartbeat/ping-pong, scaling (C10K); sticky session khi có LB.
- **Kafka:** Topic, partition, offset, consumer group; rebalance khi thêm/bớt consumer; ordering (partition key); delivery semantics (at-most-once, at-least-once, exactly-once).
- **WebRTC:** Signaling vs media; tách non-media traffic qua WebSocket để giảm tải Jitsi/server.

## Liên hệ CV

- "High-performance WebSocket server... 5,000 concurrent connections" — SYS-01 trong roadmap.
- "Resolved WebRTC server crashes by routing non-media traffic through custom WebSocket server" — SYS-02.
- Kafka (skills) — SYS-03, SYS-04 (LB cho WebSocket).

